----- Original Message -----
From: <eq_wizards-owner@onelist.com>
To: <Empress@...>
Sent: Saturday, April 17, 1999 10:17 AM
Subject: [eq_wizards] Welcome to eq_wizards@onelist.com


> Hello,
>
> Welcome to the EQ_Wizards List.
>
> This list is intended to let Wizards help Wizards. There are no hard and
> fast rules here, just try to keep postings some what on the topic of
Wizards
> and Everquest.
>
> This list is NOT moderated so there are a couple of things i would like
to
> ask of the community when posting to this list.
>
> 1) Please keep the language clean.
> 2) NO question is a dumb question so please don't flame or harrass people
> that ask questions which you might feel is stupid.
> 3) Some people consider posting information about Quest's , unique items
etc..
> to be Spoilers. So to respect the rights of those people, if you should
send in
>
> anything that is or may be considered a Spoiler please add **Spoiler** to
the
> subject so that anyone who doesn't want to read information on Spoilers
can
> just delete the mail.
>
> That's pretty much it. Have fun and let me know if there is anything i can
do to
>
> help you enjoy your stay more in this community.
>
> __
>
> To unsubscribe from this list, go to the ONElist web site, at
> www.onelist.com, and select the User Center link from the menu bar
> on the left. This menu will also let you change your subscription
> between digest and normal mode.
>
>
> Thanks,
> Saleen
>
